* Dinobot noticed Tavatron's hand on his shoulder and how gentle it was but 
then growled and shrugged it off, he hated to admit it but compassion was 
unnerving to him. He wasn't scared of it, it just felt strange and alien to 
him. A feeling that he wasn't use to and doubted that he would ever really 
know.
He looked at the screen and scrolled down, that was when he came to 
Megatron's profile.
Dinobot growled deeply and snarled, he shut off the screen and slammed it 
back down...the last thing he needed to see was the very bot that had killed 
him!! (the comp's like a laptop.)
He looked away then stood up, he had seen enough for that day!
Dinobot walked to the doorway and looked out at the doors, he would give 
anything to have Megatron's head in his hands. He'd bury it 7 feet under and 
leave it there!
He growled again and clenched his fist, the raptor claw digging into his 
palm and causing mech fluid to drip onto the floor.
Dinobot closed his optics and opened his hand, he then looked at his 
bleeding palm and sighed...*

" It would be wise for you to get some rest before the battle, it could be a 
long one."
